<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:15:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于中国经济增长放缓，西门子医疗未能实现第三季度预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-misses-q3-expectations-due-slow-china-2024-07-31/</link><description>德国医疗技术公司西门子医疗 (Siemens Healthineers) 周三报告称，由于中国订单持续延迟，第三季度销售额和盈利低于预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:31:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-misses-q3-expectations-due-slow-china-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，美国对外国芯片设备出口到中国的新规定豁免了一些盟友</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-us-rule-foreign-chip-equipment-exports-china-exempt-some-allies-sources-say-2024-07-31/</link><description>两位熟悉该规则的消息人士称，拜登政府计划下个月公布一项新规则，该规则将扩大美国阻止某些国家向中国芯片制造商出口半导体制造设备的权力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:29:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-us-rule-foreign-chip-equipment-exports-china-exempt-some-allies-sources-say-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行股价因 30 亿美元回购而上涨；上半年利润持平超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-reports-flat-first-half-profit-beats-estimates-2024-07-31/</link><description>汇丰控股周三承诺回购 30 亿美元的股票，这是提振低迷股价的新尝试，此前汇丰控股报告称，由于财富管理业务增长，上半年利润稳定，中国房地产亏损收窄。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 04:19:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-reports-flat-first-half-profit-beats-estimates-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行任命乔纳森·宾厄姆为临时首席财务官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-names-jonathan-bingham-interim-cfo-2024-07-31/</link><description>汇丰控股周三任命 Jonathan Bingham 为其临时集团首席财务官，自 9 月 2 日起生效。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 04:15:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-names-jonathan-bingham-interim-cfo-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国共产党开除中石油前董事长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-former-cnpc-chairman-party-secretary-2024-07-31/</link><description>官方媒体周三称，中国执政党共产党以违纪为由，对国有企业中国石油天然气集团公司（CNPC）原董事长、党委书记王宜林给予开除党籍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-former-cnpc-chairman-party-secretary-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国疲软的工厂PMI暴露了出口巨头的痛点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-july-factory-activity-shrinks-services-grow-more-slowly-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三的一项官方调查显示，由于工厂努力应对新订单下降和价格低廉的问题，中国7月份制造业活动跌至五个月低点，这表明这个世界生产大国的下半年将陷入困境。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-july-factory-activity-shrinks-services-grow-more-slowly-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月非制造业活动扩张放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-july-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三的一份官方工厂调查显示，中国7月份非制造业活动扩张放缓，这表明国内服务需求放缓，并加剧了房地产行业长达数年的危机的严重程度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:44:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-july-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>7月份中国制造业活动延续跌势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-manufacturing-activity-extends-decline-july-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三的一份官方工厂调查显示，中国7月份制造业活动连续第三个月萎缩，这增强了人们对北京将需要推出更多刺激措施的预期，因为旷日持久的房地产危机和就业不稳定拖累了经济增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-manufacturing-activity-extends-decline-july-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中方就中美会晤言论向日方提出抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-official-protests-japans-negative-remarks-meeting-with-us-chinese-foreign-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，北京已就日美会晤期间发表的涉华负面言论向东京表达不满。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-official-protests-japans-negative-remarks-meeting-with-us-chinese-foreign-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗哈马斯领导人被杀后油价反弹，但中国限制涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-claws-back-some-losses-after-israel-retaliates-against-hezbollah-2024-07-31/</link><description>哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在伊朗被杀加剧中东紧张局势后，周三石油期货从七周低点反弹逾一美元/桶，但由于对中国需求疲软的担忧，价格仍面临压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-claws-back-some-losses-after-israel-retaliates-against-hezbollah-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>力拓对大量铜采购持开放态度，但对市场过热持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rio-tinto-reports-largely-flat-first-half-profit-2024-07-30/</link><description>力拓首席执行官雅各布·施陶霍姆(Jakob Stausholm)周三在讨论上半年业绩时表示，力拓可能会考虑进行大规模收购，但它必须提供在火热的铜市场中很难找到的价值。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rio-tinto-reports-largely-flat-first-half-profit-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：今年市场最重要的一天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-30/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 21:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪探索进入加拿大汽车市场-监管备案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-explores-canadian-auto-market-entry-regulatory-filing-2024-07-30/</link><description>根据本月早些时候提交的一份监管文件，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪正在寻求进入加拿大汽车市场，尽管加拿大官员正在考虑对从中国进口的汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:19:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-explores-canadian-auto-market-entry-regulatory-filing-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>二号外交官表示，美国必须采取更多措施反击中国的行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二表示，华盛顿必须采取更多措施来对抗中国的行动，包括其建立军事基地的战略以及在非洲开采稀土矿的战略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国马拉松选手准备在巴黎与职业选手并肩作战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/marathon-chinese-runner-ready-deliver-alongside-pros-paris-2024-07-30/</link><description>栾玉帅每天要花12个小时送包裹。之后，他穿上运动鞋，开始一天中他最喜欢的部分——马拉松训练。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/marathon-chinese-runner-ready-deliver-alongside-pros-paris-2024-07-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>